        <Nerangs id="ritualNerangs">
            <ab>VytVrS0.4 (mss. 5010, 5020, 5030, 5100, 5105, 5116):</ab>
            <ab class="ab_indent">
                ōy kē zōtīh kāmēd kardan dast pad pādyāb kardan ō ī gāh ī ātrawaxšān šudan war ō ī ātaxšgāh ud barsom kardan pad sē aṣ̌emwōhū har čahār kustag bē šōyišn</ab>
            <ab class="ab_indent">
                "The one who wishes to perform in the office of <em>zōt</em> should clean his hands with <em>pādyāb</em>, go to the place of the <em>ātrawaxš</em>, facing the <em>ātaxšgāh</em> 
                and the <em>barsom</em> and with three Aṣ̌əm Vōhū he has to clean each one of its four sides (of the <em>ātaxšgāh</em>)."</ab>
        </Nerangs>
    </Ritual>
